    {
      "id": "long_technical_paragraph",
      "category": "long_form",
      "audio_path": "tests/fixtures/audio/long_technical_paragraph.wav",
      "ground_truth": "我們目前的架構是用Qwen3 ASR做語音辨識，然後接一個Qwen3 4B的polish模型做後處理。整個pipeline的延遲大概在3到5秒左右，主要瓶頸在decoder。我想評估看看MediaTek的Breeze ASR模型是否能改善辨識品質，特別是在中英混合的場景。",
      "must_contain": ["ASR", "pipeline", "decoder", "Breeze"],
      "must_not_contain": [],
      "note": "長段落技術描述 — 多個英文術語 + 多句結構"
    },
    {
      "id": "fact_int4_slower",
      "category": "semantic",
      "audio_path": "tests/fixtures/audio/fact_int4_slower.wav",
